&gt;&gt;
&gt; In first you have to comment 2 beans and uncomment only one bean. The 2
&gt; beans you have to comment them are as follows:
&gt;
&gt; The first one
&gt; ------------------
&gt;
&gt; &lt;!--&lt;bean id=&quot;longerOverrides&quot; class=&quot;org.springframework.beans.factory.config.
&gt;
&gt;     &lt;property name=&quot;properties&quot;&gt;
&gt;
&gt;       &lt;props&gt;
&gt;
&gt;         &lt;prop key=&quot;seeds.textSource.value&quot;&gt;
&gt;
&gt; # URLS HERE
&gt;
&gt;         &lt;/prop&gt;
&gt;
&gt;       &lt;/props&gt;
&gt;
&gt;     &lt;/property&gt;
&gt;
&gt;   &lt;/bean&gt;  --&gt;
&gt;
&gt; The second one
&gt; ----------------------
&gt;
&gt; &lt;!--&lt;bean id=&quot;seeds&quot; class=&quot;org.archive.modules.seeds.TextSeedModule&quot;&gt;
&gt;
&gt;           &lt;property name=&quot;textSource&quot;&gt;
&gt;
&gt;             &lt;bean class=&quot;org.archive.spring.ConfigString&quot;&gt;
&gt;
&gt;               &lt;property name=&quot;value&quot;&gt;
&gt;
&gt;                 &lt;value&gt;
&gt;
&gt; # [see override above]
&gt;
&gt;                 &lt;/value&gt;
&gt;
&gt;               &lt;/property&gt;
&gt;
&gt;             &lt;/bean&gt;
&gt;
&gt;           &lt;/property&gt;
&gt;
&gt;   &lt;property name=&#39;sourceTagSeeds&#39; value=&#39;false&#39;/&gt;
&gt;
&gt;   &lt;/bean&gt;--&gt;
&gt;
&gt; After that you have to uncomment the following bean:
&gt;
&gt;   &lt;bean id=&quot;seeds&quot; class=&quot;org.archive.modules.seeds.TextSeedModule&quot;&gt;
&gt;
&gt;     &lt;property name=&quot;textSource&quot;&gt;
&gt;
&gt;       &lt;bean class=&quot;org.archive.spring.ConfigFile&quot;&gt;
&gt;
&gt;         &lt;property name=&quot;path&quot; value=&quot;seeds.txt&quot; /&gt;
&gt;
&gt;       &lt;/bean&gt;
&gt;
&gt;     &lt;/property&gt;
&gt;
&gt;     &lt;property name=&#39;sourceTagSeeds&#39; value=&#39;false&#39;/&gt;
&gt;
&gt;   &lt;/bean&gt;
&gt;
&gt; Note that: I put seeds.txt in the same directory of Heritrix. You can
&gt; put it under any directory as you want, but you have to write its path
&gt; in the value as shown above.
